“新公民运动”这个名称是许志永在2012年5月发表的纲领性文章《中国新公民运动》<ref name="citizensmovement">{{cite web | author=许志永 | title=中国新公民运动 | date=May 29, 2012 | publisher=中国人权双周刊 | url=http://biweekly.hrichina.org/article/1575 | work= | pages= | accessdate= | language= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121226221847/http://biweekly.hrichina.org/article/1575 | archive-date=2012-12-26 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>中提出并正式开始使用的。

中国官方一直对新公民运动进行监控和压制，2013年7月16日新公民运动发起人[[许志永|许志永]]被拘捕<ref name="nytimes1">{{cite news | author=Chris Buckley | title=A Leading Chinese Human Rights Advocate Is Detained in Beijing | date=July 17, 2013 | publisher=NYTimes | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/18/world/asia/china-detains-a-leading-human-rights-advocate.html | work= | pages= | accessdate= | language=en | archive-date=2013-09-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130922085234/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/07/18/world/asia/china-detains-a-leading-human-rights-advocate.html | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="usatoday">{{cite news | author=Calum MacLeod | title=China silences anti-corruption activists | date=July 30, 2013 | publisher=USA Today | url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/07/30/china-corruption-prison/2590301/ | work= | pages= | accessdate= | language=en | archive-date=2013-08-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130805214125/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/world/2013/07/30/china-corruption-prison/2590301/ | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="nytimes2">{{cite news | author=Jane Perlez | title=Jailed Chinese Rights Advocate Speaks Out in Video | date=Aug 8, 2013 | publisher=NYTimes | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/09/world/asia/imprisoned-chinese-rights-advocate-urges-defiance-in-video.html | work= | pages= | accessdate= | language=en | archive-date=2013-08-12 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130812201428/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/09/world/asia/imprisoned-chinese-rights-advocate-urges-defiance-in-video.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>，2013年9月13日新公民运动发起人[[王功权|王功权]]被警方刑拘<ref>{{cite news| title =北京警方向王功权出示的传唤证被公开o| date =2013-09-13| publisher =搜狐新闻| url =http://news.sohu.com/20130913/n386554980.shtm| work =| pages =| accessdate =| language =}}{{dead link|date=2018年3月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。自2014年1月22日起许志永等案密集开庭审理，引发海内外巨大关注。新公民支持者创建新公民邮件组与公民权利关注组，继续新公民理念的推广。

==新公民精神和标识==
